    "name": "NUSNUR",
    "steam_appid": 2266500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/10d6fdc1118bc95a7be09929da90e8da.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/10d6fdc1118bc95a7be09929da90e8da.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/10d6fdc1118bc95a7be09929da90e8da.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the multiverse with different versions of <strong>NUSNUR</strong>s where every universe has its own mechanics, style, story, and lore. Observe how their lives connect and how everything ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NUSNUR</strong> is a story-based RPG with multiple endings. Gameplay begins with hack-and-slash and turn-based combat, changing with each universe. Not only your choices, but also your playstyle affect the story’s progression.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want, you can <span class=\"bb_strike\">play</span> observe the story in co-op with up to 4 players~</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>START THE ADVENTURE WITH <i>NIMBUS</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the cast of the universe of <i>Nimbus Seynasirun,</i> whose search for happiness turns into obsession of ignorance. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/871d78353c71ca2f97ed5db17a730b5a.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/871d78353c71ca2f97ed5db17a730b5a.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/871d78353c71ca2f97ed5db17a730b5a.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow her adventure and acknowledge her ideals while exploring personalities of other cast members. Observe multiple outcomes and discover different conclusions. I will be with you throughout...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/28b7adf9c6d525d7a1a0fb405d49beff.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/28b7adf9c6d525d7a1a0fb405d49beff.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/28b7adf9c6d525d7a1a0fb405d49beff.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HACK AND SLASH WITH EYE MAGIC</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a universe where your eye color decides who you are and grants you the power that can bring chaos or peace... Their eyes are pure, they are not like you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/10d546f8340c6e3fc0107a27fa449e8c.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=600 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/10d546f8340c6e3fc0107a27fa449e8c.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/10d546f8340c6e3fc0107a27fa449e8c.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TURN BASED STRATEGY AND BULLET HELL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every universe has its own twist, its own mechanics. In the universe of eyes, try to understand illusion battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/2c8664f31b89bc04fee6d93f12d83ae5.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=600 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/2c8664f31b89bc04fee6d93f12d83ae5.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/2c8664f31b89bc04fee6d93f12d83ae5.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Observe how they utilize their magic and how it affects their lives as they try to reach their goals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/20ef96e64b8af93acba899e8894e6da0.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=600 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/20ef96e64b8af93acba899e8894e6da0.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/20ef96e64b8af93acba899e8894e6da0.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CO-OP WITH YOUR FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for an adventure with your friends across the universes of <i>NUSNUR</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/7599037f292b741d7c2a182921f628e9.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/7599037f292b741d7c2a182921f628e9.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/7599037f292b741d7c2a182921f628e9.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emote all over the story for some goofy time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/4ce38a29ee5acc5b2d956062f4240c58.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=600 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/4ce38a29ee5acc5b2d956062f4240c58.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/4ce38a29ee5acc5b2d956062f4240c58.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up and observe Nimbus and her illusions as they take down anything that stands in their way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/354e00c8760cfdc413c9b0ef3a5e4cf4.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=600 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/354e00c8760cfdc413c9b0ef3a5e4cf4.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/354e00c8760cfdc413c9b0ef3a5e4cf4.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why not settle who among you would have been the greatest eye magic warrior of all time... in a bit of &quot;<i>friendly</i>&quot; imagination battle?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/59b6785998b82d4f1ed617cf95425dc8.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=600 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/59b6785998b82d4f1ed617cf95425dc8.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/59b6785998b82d4f1ed617cf95425dc8.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MYSTERY OF ALL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let us embark on this journey, and find out how everything ends...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Soul Waiter</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/8636e8731f922b6a83e71b07f7521b3a.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/8636e8731f922b6a83e71b07f7521b3a.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/8636e8731f922b6a83e71b07f7521b3a.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PURCHASE &amp; DEMO</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By <u><strong>purchasing</strong></u>, you will gain access to <strong>Chapter 1</strong> and <strong>all other main chapter</strong> releases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By <u><strong>playing DEMO</strong></u>, you get <strong>limited access to</strong> <strong>Chapter 1</strong>, &quot;<strong>imaginations</strong>&quot; are not included, and any <strong>achievements</strong> you observe will not count toward <strong>Steam achievements</strong>. However, when you switch to the full game, your story and choice progression will carry over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/7e11be4c152b0cd026b64826d3758e88.poster.avif?t=1748948207\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/7e11be4c152b0cd026b64826d3758e88.webm?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2266500/extras/7e11be4c152b0cd026b64826d3758e88.mp4?t=1748948207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
